txt.en: Ognir hunts the lands along the northern banks of the swiftwater river to the north-east of Brockbridge.
Ognir hunts the lands along the northern banks of the Swiftwater River to the north-east of Brockbridge.
Ognir has finally met his match and was hunted down and defeated by a mighty [placeholder].
The ancient troll Ognir has been defeated, and will now only lurk in the nightmares of the people of the Stonedeans.
Ognir, a troll who seems as old as the mountains nearby, has long hunted the beasts along the northern banks of the Swiftwater River.

Stories of Ognir have long been told to the children in the Stonedeans, of an ancient troll who lurks near the northern banks of the Swiftwater River. Those who hunt the lands of the Stonedeans have learned to avoid the area, or risk finding themselves hunted.
